 and QoE parameters. It is observed that DPQoAP enhances the efficiency of\nthe networking operations and adaptability of the applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Dec 2019 12:05:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-26"}
